WEBVTT

00:04:29.760 --> 00:04:31.936
I'm using your energy,

00:04:31.960 --> 00:04:37.736
and with this energy I can go
and push my body as far as I can.

00:04:37.760 --> 00:04:41.336
And then I liberate myself
from these fears.

00:04:41.360 --> 00:04:42.656
And I'm your mirror.

00:04:42.680 --> 00:04:45.960
If I can do this for myself,
you can do it for you.

00:04:46.720 --> 00:04:48.776
After Belgrade, where I was born,

00:04:48.800 --> 00:04:51.080
I went to Amsterdam.

00:04:51.440 --> 00:04:54.056
And you know, I've been doing performances

00:04:54.080 --> 00:04:56.336
since the last 40 years.

00:04:56.360 --> 00:04:57.936
And here I met Ulay,

00:04:57.960 --> 00:05:01.336
and he was the person
I actually fell in love with.